don't download this, because the program doesn't find some registry errors. i'd recommend CCleaner instead (google it). it  fixes ALL registry errors, you can choose which programs you wish to have at the startup of your computer, uninstall programs, clean your internet browser history, cookies. if something went wrong, simply restore your system easily.
and the best of all, it's COMPLETELY FREE.

dont put all your trust in Ccleaner, it misses plenty of registry errors as well. there is no perfect program to perform this task. I use both this and Ccleaner and after running ccleaner i run this and always find things that ccleaner missed, as well as vice versa.

Serial numbers wont work. When you enter the numbers, it tries to establish a connection to the company website to verify the serial number. If you deny it access, it wont register, and if you allow it internet access, it says the numbers are invalid.

My mistake, I tried the serial from the keygen on the wrong version of the program. The serials work for this version, so all is well.
